We recommended that Management ensure that the required supporting documents must be attached to the disbursement voucher prior to payment of claims for travelling expenses.

Further, submit the following information/documents for the above payment of travel claims, otherwise, the amount shall be suspended in audit.  

Travel order (duly signed by the Provincial Governor); 
Itinerary of Travel to include the details of flight such as the passengers name, date of flight, destination, airport, and other flight services included therein;
Certificate of Appearance or Back to Office Report/Narrative Report on trip undertaken/Report on Participation which shall contain among others the following information:
Highlights of the training /activity;
Pictures preferably dated;
Plan of action for knowledge sharing; and
Recommendations
Boarding Pass or its equivalent
Other necessary documents relevant to the claim

